00:43:04,963 --> 00:43:06,045
What's wrong with him?

822
00:43:06,131 --> 00:43:07,167
NORTON:
No, nothing, nothing.

823
00:43:07,341 --> 00:43:09,710
Watch the procedural bars

824
00:43:09,843 --> 00:43:12,555
on the 208.

