00:43:28,362 --> 00:43:30,026
Alex's brain receives
the information

834
00:43:30,115 --> 00:43:32,734
and decides what to do with it
based on his emotional...

835
00:43:32,867 --> 00:43:33,733
- Rig ht.
-cognitive abilities,

836
00:43:33,868 --> 00:43:34,860
like any man would.

837
00:43:34,953 --> 00:43:36,035
- Right.
- Then the brain

838
00:43:36,121 --> 00:43:38,911
relates this to the AI module,

839
00:43:38,998 --> 00:43:40,365
- Yeah.
-and, uh...

840
00:43:40,459 --> 00:43:42,041
Like, you know, a year later.

841
00:43:42,126 --> 00:43:43,414
And our computers
finish the job.

842
00:43:43,544 --> 00:43:46,869
Raymond, you-you wanted
a man inside a machine,

843
00:43:46,964 --> 00:43:48,799
