interfere with the system.

847
00:43:55,265 --> 00:43:56,597
Okay, but, Dennett...

848
00:43:56,724 --> 00:43:59,095
I've got to give
the American people

849
00:43:59,228 --> 00:44:00,468
something they can root for.

850
00:44:00,604 --> 00:44:02,095
Something aspirational, right?

851
00:44:02,230 --> 00:44:03,722
They have to believe
in this thing.

852
00:44:03,816 --> 00:44:05,102
"Pretty good," that's not...

853
00:44:05,191 --> 00:44:07,230
I don't know how to sell "okay."

854
00:44:07,319 --> 00:44:09,278
We, you and I, have
got a release date,

855
00:44:09,405 --> 00:44:11,614
