00:45:01,249 --> 00:45:02,160
I love it.

874
00:45:02,292 --> 00:45:03,955
Mm.

875
00:45:04,127 --> 00:45:05,665
Okay.

876
00:45:05,796 --> 00:45:08,382
I'm gonna put you to
sleep now, Alex, okay?

877
00:45:08,507 --> 00:45:10,374
Okay.

878
00:45:10,509 --> 00:45:12,502
Now, put him under, Kim.

879
00:45:14,055 --> 00:45:16,048
(computer beeps,
