most of the time.

904
00:46:18,538 --> 00:46:20,531
(sighs)
Make him more, uh...

905
00:46:20,623 --> 00:46:22,707
tactical.

906
00:46:22,792 --> 00:46:24,501
Make him look, uh...

907
