00:46:42,521 --> 00:46:44,513
(brakes squeaking)

911
00:46:52,406 --> 00:46:54,399
(thud)

912
00:46:54,491 --> 00:46:56,199
(thudding, whirring)

913
00:47:02,833 --> 00:47:05,829
(thudding, whirring continue)

914
00:47:05,962 --> 00:47:08,797
- Alex. -He looks like
a billion dollars.

915
00:47:08,922 --> 00:47:11,587
2.6 billion.

916
00:47:11,675 --> 00:47:13,965
Raymond Sellars.

