00:48:30,840 --> 00:48:32,833
I've been through a lot.

944
00:48:36,805 --> 00:48:38,593
All right.

945
00:48:40,350 --> 00:48:42,092
I say we go on three.

946
00:48:42,226 --> 00:48:43,811
Three.

947
00:48:51,403 --> 00:48:54,398
