00:49:05,375 --> 00:49:06,834
How's it going down there?

950
00:49:08,838 --> 00:49:12,585
Whatever you do,
don't get shot in the face.

951
00:49:14,385 --> 00:49:16,469
Wow.

952
00:49:25,981 --> 00:49:28,395
♪♪

