977
00:50:36,804 --> 00:50:38,045
making him think he's doing

978
00:50:38,180 --> 00:50:39,672
what our computers
are actually doing.

979
00:50:39,807 --> 00:50:42,347
I mean, Alex believes,
right now, he is in control,

980
00:50:42,435 --> 00:50:44,553
