982
00:50:55,698 --> 00:50:56,780
Crap.

983
00:51:03,498 --> 00:51:05,490
♪♪

984
00:51:13,633 --> 00:51:15,626
♪♪

985
00:51:17,846 --> 00:51:19,554
LIZ:
So you've circumvented the law

986
00:51:19,681 --> 00:51:21,845
by creating a machine
that thinks it's a man,

987
00:51:21,933 --> 00:51:23,049
but that's illegal.

988
00:51:23,142 --> 00:51:25,260
- The...
- No... no, no, no.

989
00:51:25,394 --> 00:51:28,561
It's a machine
that thinks it's Alex Murphy,

990
00:51:28,648 --> 00:51:31,849
