1007
00:52:34,425 --> 00:52:37,466
I'm sure hers is, too.

1008
00:52:37,553 --> 00:52:38,669
(whirrs)

1009
00:52:38,804 --> 00:52:40,797
You're gonna do fine.

1010
00:52:42,183 --> 00:52:44,051
(whirrs)

