00:53:54,173 --> 00:53:56,258
(footsteps thudding)

1024
00:54:12,108 --> 00:54:14,101
(sighs)

1025
00:54:22,244 --> 00:54:23,907
(whirrs)

1026
00:54:28,250 --> 00:54:30,539
(footsteps thudding)

1027
00:54:44,683 --> 00:54:46,142
Hi, Dad.

1028
00:54:50,105 --> 00:54:52,315
