1051
00:56:38,092 --> 00:56:39,755
I'm sorry, Alex.

1052
00:56:39,886 --> 00:56:41,423
Starting tomorrow,

1053
00:56:41,512 --> 00:56:43,973
I'm gonna take down Vallon
and his whole damn crew.

1054
00:56:44,098 --> 00:56:46,091
I was waiting
to hear you say that.

1055
00:56:49,687 --> 00:56:51,806
Least I know you're
the right color now.

1056
00:56:51,940 --> 00:56:53,933
(chuckles)

1057
00:56:57,028 --> 00:56:59,021
(thudding, whirring)

